Installation:

    git clone https://github.com/blumbri/dotfiles.git ~/dotfiles

Create symlinks:

    ln -s ~/dotfiles/vim ~/.vim
    ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc   ~/.vimrc

    ln -s ~/dotfiles/tmux/tmux.conf ~/.tmux.conf

    ln -s ~/dotfiles/zsh/zshrc     ~/.zshrc
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/zsh/zshenv    ~/.zshenv
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/zsh/zprofile  ~/.zprofile
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/zsh/oh-my-zsh ~/.oh-my-zsh

    ln -s ~/dotfiles/xorg/Xresources  ~/.Xresources
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/xorg/Xmodmap     ~/.Xmodmap
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/xorg/xbindkeysrc ~/.xbindkeysrc
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/xorg/xinitrc     ~/.xinitrc
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/xorg/xinitrc.d   ~/.xinitrc.d

    ln -s ~/dotfiles/i3/i3       ~/.config/i3
    ln -s ~/dotfiles/i3/i3status ~/.config/i3status

    ln -s ~/dotfiles/conky ~/.config/conky

Prepare oh-my-zsh:

    git clone https://github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh.git ~/.oh-my-zsh

Prepare neobundle (vim-plugins):

    curl https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Shougo/neobundle.vim/master/bin/install.sh | sh
    vim +NeoBundleInstall! +qall
